Procedimentos docker
-Instalar docker
	-https://docs.docker.com/install/linux/docker-ce/ubuntu/

	 sudo apt install gnupg2 pass (para logar com docker)

    - docker-compose up com arquivo do projeto
    ServerName atos.click em apache2.conf
    a2enmod rewrite


//driver postgres
apt-get install -y libpq-dev \
  && docker-php-ext-configure pgsql -with-pgsql=/usr/local/pgsql \
  && docker-php-ext-install pdo pdo_pgsql pgsql


pecl install mongodb

docker-php-ext-enable mongodb


----Apartir de 24/02/2020 apenas executar docker-compose up -d para Subir imagens do dockerHub-----


